reviews: Not as described, very poor quality.
Ordered a 2XL and ended up gifting it to my ten year old, forty five pound niece. She loves it, but definitely not made for adults.
Waited 13 years, and it’s phenomenal. Duh.

The sweater overall is decent quality, but I ordered a 2XL so it fit really loose..it fits like a medium/large. I’m angry for all my curvy ladies who won’t be able to enjoy this hoodie at this price. 2XL for ants I guess.
Exactly as described, and arrived on time
